body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Nature     Plants     Alien Plants                Alien Plants      Unfortunately, many plants found in the park are invading the native ecosystem, choking out the native vegetation and damaging archeological sites. The park is battling these alien invaders with pesticides, vegetation removal and out-planting native species.
